# Client Admin Dashboard — Phase 1 Walkthrough

## Summary

Implemented all 6 core features from the PRD for the Dallah Client Admin Dashboard. The dashboard is fully functional with MSW mock data, bilingual support (en/ar), and all forms validated.

## What Was Built

### Dashboard Layout
- Responsive sidebar navigation with 5 links + user info + logout + language switcher
- Quick-action cards on the home page linking to each feature
- Mobile-friendly with hamburger menu

### Features Implemented

| Feature | Route | Status |
|---------|-------|--------|
| Add User | `/dashboard/users/add` | ✅ Complete |
| Bulk Import | `/dashboard/users/bulk` | ✅ Complete |
| Enrollments (CRUD) | `/dashboard/enrollments` | ✅ Complete |
| Attendance | `/dashboard/attendance` | ✅ Complete |

### Files Created

**UI Components** (6 shadcn/ui components):
- [card.tsx](file:///home/hafez/aanaab/ai-first/src/components/ui/card.tsx), [select.tsx](file:///home/hafez/aanaab/ai-first/src/components/ui/select.tsx), [dialog.tsx](file:///home/hafez/aanaab/ai-first/src/components/ui/dialog.tsx), [badge.tsx](file:///home/hafez/aanaab/ai-first/src/components/ui/badge.tsx), [separator.tsx](file:///home/hafez/aanaab/ai-first/src/components/ui/separator.tsx), [alert.tsx](file:///home/hafez/aanaab/ai-first/src/components/ui/alert.tsx)

